      "value": "<p>When you choose this domain at 1st level, you gain proficiency in the Intimidation or Persuasion skill (your choice), and can use your Wisdom Modifier instead of Charisma for the chosen skill. If you already have both of these skill proficiencies, you gain proficiency in one skill of your choice from the list of skills available to clerics at 1st level.</p><blockquote><p><strong>When you gain this feature, you will have to manually update your character sheet with your chosen proficiency.  It is recommended that you edit this feature to note your selection.</strong></p></blockquote>",
